## Recommended Reading

Books and articles that have shaped my design thinking.

- **"Don't Make Me Think" by Steve Krug** — The classic guide to web usability
- **"Content Design" by Sarah Winters** — Essential reading for content strategy
- **"Articulating Design Decisions" by Tom Greever** — How to communicate design rationale to stakeholders
- **"Mismatch" by Kat Holmes** — A powerful framework for inclusive design
- **"Continuous Discovery Habits" by Teresa Torres** — Modern product discovery practices

---

## Favorite Tools

The tools I reach for on every project.

- **Figma** — Interface design and prototyping
- **Dovetail** — Research repository and analysis
- **Maze** — Unmoderated usability testing
- **Notion** — Documentation and project management
- **Loom** — Async communication and walkthroughs

